  {
    "id": "self_care_during_period",
    "title": "Creating A Self-Care Routine During Your Period",
    "category": "Mental Wellness",
    "readTime": "7 min read",
    "summary": "Build healthy habits that support emotional wellbeing, comfort, and relaxation during menstruation.",
    "content": "# Creating A Self-Care Routine During Your Period\n\nPeriods are not only a physical experience. They can also affect mood, energy levels, motivation, and emotional wellbeing.\n\nCreating a simple self-care routine can help you feel more supported throughout your cycle.\n\n## What Is Self-Care?\n\nSelf-care means intentionally taking actions that support your physical and emotional wellbeing.\n\nIt does not have to be expensive or complicated.\n\nSmall daily habits often make the biggest difference.\n\n## Listen To Your Energy Levels\n\nMany people experience lower energy during menstruation.\n\nInstead of pushing yourself excessively, consider:\n\n• Taking short breaks\n• Reducing unnecessary stress\n• Prioritizing important tasks\n• Allowing yourself additional rest\n\n## Create A Comfort Routine\n\nComfort strategies may include:\n\n• Warm drinks\n• Comfortable clothing\n• Gentle stretching\n• Reading\n• Listening to calming music\n\n## Journaling For Emotional Awareness\n\nWriting down thoughts and emotions can help identify patterns throughout your cycle.\n\nYou may begin noticing:\n\n• Energy changes\n• Mood changes\n• Sleep patterns\n• Stress triggers\n\n## Nourish Your Body\n\nSupport your wellbeing with:\n\n• Balanced meals\n• Fruits and vegetables\n• Protein-rich foods\n• Adequate hydration\n\n## Digital Self-Care\n\nSocial media and constant notifications can sometimes increase stress.\n\nConsider taking short breaks from screens when feeling overwhelmed.\n\n## Create Your Personal Period Wellness Plan\n\nAsk yourself:\n\n• What helps me relax?\n• What gives me energy?\n• What increases stress?\n• What makes me feel supported?\n\nUse these answers to build a routine that works for you.\n\n## Quick Summary\n\nA period self-care routine can support emotional wellbeing, reduce stress, and help you feel more connected to your body's needs throughout your cycle."
